{"pagelen": 50, "values": [{"update": {"description": "`catkin_make_isolated --install` currently fails, as documented in #372. This fix installs the plugins to lib instead of a subfolder of lib. A namespace is applied to plugin name, to avoid polluting the lib folder. Also, the headers for drcsim_gazebo_plugins were not being installed.", "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "67d6b1f27794", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/67d6b1f27794.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/67d6b1f27794"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "drcsim_3.1"}}, "reason": "On second thought, I shouldn't rename the plugin. I'll try to figure out a better solution.", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "0c0cf6c236f9", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/commit/0c0cf6c236f9.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/commits/0c0cf6c236f9"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "branch": {"name": "issue_372"}}, "state": "DECLINED", "author": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "date": "2013-11-12T17:23:24.634839+00:00"}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409/comments/782889.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409/_/diff#comment-782889"}}, "parent": {"id": 782300, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409/comments/782300.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409/_/diff#comment-782300"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}, "content": {"raw": "It doesn't feel clean to me, but without this fix, isolated builds don't work (the builds have to be isolated when I build against a custom gazebo branch). I'm open to suggestions.\n\nThe problem is that drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins needs to find the DRCVehiclePlugin library, but since it wasn't installed to `lib`; it can't  be found.\n\nAny ideas?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>It doesn't feel clean to me, but without this fix, isolated builds don't work (the builds have to be isolated when I build against a custom gazebo branch). I'm open to suggestions.</p>\n<p>The problem is that drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins needs to find the DRCVehiclePlugin library, but since it wasn't installed to <code>lib</code>; it can't  be found.</p>\n<p>Any ideas?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-11-07T06:37:53.627943+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": "2013-11-07T06:37:53.637157+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 782889}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}}, {"approval": {"date": "2013-11-07T02:16:55.928857+00:00", "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}, "user": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409/comments/782300.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409/_/diff#comment-782300"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/pullrequests/409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/pull-requests/409"}}, "title": "Fix #372: catkin_make_isolated --install"}, "content": {"raw": "It's a little odd to relocate (and rename) some libs to satisfy a particular build workflow.  But if it's an important workflow and this is the best fix, so be it.\n\nDo you know why we don't have the same problem with the shared objects built in `drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins`?  They're still being installed to `<prefix>/lib/drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins/plugins`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>It's a little odd to relocate (and rename) some libs to satisfy a particular build workflow.  But if it's an important workflow and this is the best fix, so be it.</p>\n<p>Do you know why we don't have the same problem with the shared objects built in <code>drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins</code>?  They're still being installed to <code>&lt;prefix&gt;/lib/drcsim_gazebo_ros_plugins/plugins</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-11-07T02:16:54.372604+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "updated_on